content:
Analyze Your Data

Salesforce Analytics Tools include Reports and Dashboards, Data Cloud Reports and Dashboards, and CRM Analytics.

Get Started Using CRM Analytics by Setting Up the Platform, Integrating Data, and Exploring Visualized Data.

Gain Insights on Data Directly at Source using CRM Analytics. Build Customizable Dashboards and Apps to Share with Business Users.

Deploy Industry-Specific Apps like Analytics for Automotive, Communications-Business, and Consumer.

Enable CRM Analytics in your Salesforce org before creating an app from the Analytics for Communications - Consumer template.

REQUIRED EDITIONS: Available in Developer edition and for an extra cost in Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited editions.

Assign Administrator Permissions for Analytics for Communications - Consumer. 

Grant Permission to the Analytics Integration User and Set Field-Level Security.

Import Payment and Usage Data to enable creation of the Analytics for Communications - Consumer app.

Create and Share Apps from Templates like CRM Analytics Prebuilt Apps, Intelligent Analytics Apps, Tableau, Unified Analytics Experiences, and Einstein Discovery.
title: Enable Salesforce CRM Analytics
